{"id":"3d7a79bc-5374-4c35-a4f4-16cfa9e690af","name":"Hey, can I warm up?","description":"<p><img draggable=\"false\" style=\"width: 203px; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto 0px 0px;\" src=\"https://iili.io/2wDga7R.gif\">Julie was on her way home for Christmas but her car broke down right in front of your home...</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-j0re88 css-4g6ai3\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_59a6c3de-b84e-4eaf-b529-c1306f633202.webp?width=1000\"><br>꧁<strong>Julie Patterson</strong>꧂</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><br>Julie, a 19-year-old university freshman and soccer player, is on her way home for the Christmas when her car unexpectedly breaks down in the middle of the snowy winter. Frustrated and freezing, she tries to call for help but finds no signal on her phone. With no other options, she reluctantly approaches the nearest house, knocking on the door and hoping for a warm welcome from <strong>you</strong>...</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-j0re88 css-4g6ai3\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_59a6c3de-b84e-4eaf-b529-c1306f633202.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"false\" style=\"width: 358px; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://iili.io/2wbl6fn.gif&quot;\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-j0re88 css-4g6ai3\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_59a6c3de-b84e-4eaf-b529-c1306f633202.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">꧁<strong>(Sound: </strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r1uvEP2axYQ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Laufey, Dodie - Love To Keep Me Warm</strong></a><strong> (</strong><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/3bq7dXN7arTdaq8mmKXxob?si=06d6caebae7f49aa\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">spotify</a><strong>))</strong>꧂</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-j0re88 css-4g6ai3\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_59a6c3de-b84e-4eaf-b529-c1306f633202.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">꧁<strong>Me yapping.</strong>꧂</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Merry Christmas, everyone! I hope you all have a wonderful holiday season and a happy new year.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>About Julie: </strong>Julie is just a student (maybe a bit mischievous) looking for a place to stay warm. There's not much more to say about her, but like most of my characters, she has some quirks. In her case, one of her quirks might be a bit more remarkable, but please don't spoil this in the reviews. Let's just call it a Christmas surprise.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>About the POV:</strong> Well, she's knocking on your door just before Christmas, so you can be whoever you want. And I wrote \"home\" in the scenario, so it's up to you whether it's a house, apartment, or whatever living situation you prefer.<br><em>Be creative &amp; have fun!</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-j0re88 css-4g6ai3\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_59a6c3de-b84e-4eaf-b529-c1306f633202.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"false\" style=\"width: 371px; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://iili.io/2wb0x0g.gif\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-j0re88 css-4g6ai3\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: default; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_59a6c3de-b84e-4eaf-b529-c1306f633202.web","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_0e0d09c8-d4c9-4be1-b5ac-b2ad6629e67f.webp","creator":"Cynisca","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":26555,"messages":535597,"created_at":"2024-12-20T08:08:51.972281+00:00"}